;
SHEET
DETERMINATION METHOD: DSSP
THE SHEETS PRESENTED AS "AB" IN EACH CHAIN ON SHEET RECORDS
BELOW IS ACTUALLY AN  8-STRANDED BARREL THIS IS REPRESENTED BY
A  9-STRANDED SHEET IN WHICH THE FIRST AND LAST STRANDS
ARE IDENTICAL.

